dc_description_s: This data represents boundaries for private school within the state of Wisconsin in 2023. [This dataset includes point location data for private schools in Wisconsin. The points are placed on or near each school building's centroid. School data was pulled from the Department of Public Instruction's schools database on February 16, 2023. This data gets updated biannually so for more up-to-date information, please visit the DPI public school directory.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-wi-dpi.opendata.arcgis.com/
